cs/faq-31","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"1 CPU 核心，512MB 内存，10GB 存储"},"279":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-32","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"Docker 和 Docker Compose"},"280":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-33","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"支持 PostgreSQL 的环境（pgvector 扩展通过 Docker 自动安装）"},"281":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-34","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据存储在哪里","content":"在你的自己的服务器上。所有数据（笔记、图片、视频）都保存在你控制的硬件上。存储可以是本地磁盘或 Cloudflare R2（兼容 S3）。"},"282":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-35","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#能导出数据吗","content":"API 支持通过标准 REST 端点获取所有笔记、日记和资源。管理面板也提供健康和统计信息。"},"283":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-36","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据加密吗","content":"**传输中**：是的，通过反向代理配置 HTTPS 后加密（参见部署指南）"},"284":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-37","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据加密吗","content":"**静态存储**：数据库级别加密取决于你的 PostgreSQL 配置。文件存储按原样保存在磁盘或 R2 上"},"285":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-38","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据加密吗","content":"**密码**：使用 bcrypt 哈希存储"},"286":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-39","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#mosaic-支持多用户吗","content":"目前 Mosaic 主要面向个人或小团队使用。多个用户共享同一个服务器实例。"},"287":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-40","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#可以离线使用吗","content":"移动端使用 SQLite 在本地缓存数据。你可以在离线时查看和编辑笔记——重新连接服务器后会自动同步。"},"288":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-41","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#支持哪些-ai-模型","content":"任何兼容 OpenAI API 或 Anthropic API 的模型。包括 OpenAI（GPT-4、GPT-4o）、Anthropic（Claude）、Ollama（本地）以及提供兼容端点的任何服务商。"},"289":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-42","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#同步如何工作","content":"Mosaic 使用基于时间戳的游标协议。每种实体类型（笔记、日记、资源、机器人）跟踪其最后更新时间。移动端客户端从上次同步游标处拉取变更并在本地合并。"},"290":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-43","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#冲突怎么办","content":"Mosaic 采用\"最后写入者胜出\"策略，基于 `updated_at` 时间戳。保留最近的更改。"},"291":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-44","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器无法启动","content":"检查 PostgreSQL 是否运行且可访问"},"292":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-45","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器无法启动","content":"验证 `DATABASE_URL` 是否正确"},"293":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-46","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器无法启动","content":"确保端口未被占用（默认：8080）"},"294":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-47","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器无法启动","content":"查看服务器日志：`docker compose logs mosaic-server`"},"295":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-48","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#移动端无法连接","content":"确保服务器地址正确（含端口号）"},"296":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-49","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#移动端无法连接","content":"检查服务器是否可从你的网络访问"},"297":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-50","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#移动端无法连接","content":"验证防火墙规则允许连接"},"298":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-51","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#移动端无法连接","content":"在同一网络时，使用服务器的局域网 IP 地址"},"299":{"id":"/zh/docs/getting-started","page_id":"/zh/docs/getting-started","type":"page","content":"快速开始","breadcrumbs":["Docs"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh/docs/getting-started"},"300":{"id":"/zh/docs/getting-started-0","page_id":"/zh/docs/getting-started","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/getting-started","content":"部署和使用 Mosaic"},"301":{"id":"/zh/docs/getting-started-1","page_id":"/zh/docs/getting-started","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh/docs/getting-started#快速开始","content":"快速开始"},"302":{"id":"/zh/docs/getting-started-2","page_id":"/zh/docs/getting-started","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh/docs/getting-started#前提条件","content":"前提条件